</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>用消費券搭車賺到盡　WeChat Pay HK 入閘即享額外獎賞</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/20/wechat-pay-hk-mtr-deal/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=wechat-pay-hk-mtr-deal</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 20 May 2022 09:02:53 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[WeChat Pay HK]]></category><category><![CDATA[消費券]]></category><category><![CDATA[港鐵]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099460</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>疫情稍為放緩，不少人都已經需要正常搭車返工，消費券正好用來抵消這方面的開支。不過其實還可以簡單獲得更多優惠，今次我們就來試試用 WeChat Pay HK 入閘額外賺盡優惠吧。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="color: #000000;">疫情稍為放緩，不少市民都已經需要正常搭車返工外出，消費券正好用在車費上。現在可以使用電子支付乘車，仲有一些簡單方法可以獲得更多優惠，今次我們就來試試用 WeChat Pay HK 入閘搭港鐵實測點樣額外賺盡優惠啦！</span><br /><span style="color: #000000;"><span id="more-1099460"></span></span></p><h2><span style="color: #000000;">出門逐漸頻繁搭車要精明</span></h2><p><span style="color: #000000;">最近無論返工還是出街食飯都開始回復正常，而消費券配合電子支付工具而家搭港鐵都可以用到，相當方便。WeChat Pay HK 作為其中一個可以接收消費券和入閘乘車嘅電子支付工具，是一個不錯的選擇，新用戶仲可以額外賺多 $50，今次沙律就來實測一下如何賺盡優惠！</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY4.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY4.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY4-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;">首先需要在 WeChat Pay HK 「服務」頁面，確認自己的錢包地區是「香港」，然後在下面選擇「乘車碼」，開通港鐵乘車碼。你可以選擇從 WeChat Pay HK 餘款或信用卡支付車費。簡單幾個步驟就已經開通成功，只要開啟乘車碼畫面，一掃就可以入閘。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><h2><span style="color: #000000;">消費券搭車自動扣款</span></h2><p><span style="color: #000000;">如果要用消費券搭港鐵，只需要在同樣的「服務」頁面，按「政府消費券」，然後繼續開啟「消費券用於『港鐵乘車碼』自動扣款服務」選項，之後每次使用乘車碼入閘，都會自動扣去消費券的餘額。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;">如果是新用戶，在 「優惠專區」輸入優惠碼「MTR50」就可以額外獲得總值 $50 電子現金券用來搭港鐵！如果是現有用戶，只要做齊三個狂賞印任務，就可以換 $5 電子現金券搭港鐵，無論返工還是放假都可以善用消費券和 ＷeChat Pay HK 的優惠去不同目的地。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><h2><span style="color: #000000;">日行一善做公益</span></h2><p><span style="color: #000000;">WeChat Pay HK 以及騰訊基金會最近更發起「日行一善」慈善活動，所有用戶每日以 WeChat Pay HK 完成首筆消費（包括搭車）都可以得到一個公益印花，用戶可從 3 個慈善機構選擇其中一個項目捐贈印花，消費同時做善事，慳錢又有意義。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-768x768.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
