 1 個耳機插口和 1 個 HDMI 2.0 插口。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1100363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145853_1.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="600" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145853_1.jpeg 800w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145853_1-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145853_1-768x576.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>音響方面，它內置了 B&amp;O 的 4 個高級立體聲喇叭，以及 3 個內置收音咪，確保視像會議和多媒體應用都有優秀的聲音質素。其重量也只有約 1 KG，便攜出外相當方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1100364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145920_1.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="600" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145920_1.jpeg 800w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145920_1-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/c08145920_1-768x576.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><h2>官方商店預購優惠</h2><p>新的 HP Elite Dragonfly G3 將在 7 月初正式推出，而如果預先訂購的話，在官方網站就提供了 HK$2,000 的折扣優惠，只需要 HK$16,488 就可以入手最新機款，而且更免費送原廠 HP 藍牙耳機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1100531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501.jpg" alt="" width="1867" height="593" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501-694x220.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501-1280x407.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501-768x244.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/234125123-2022-05-18-112501-1536x488.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>有興趣入手的話，可以到官方網站訂購：<a href="